-- Metorex Copper Output From Ruashi in Congo to Drop 20% in December Quarter
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-12-01T06:30:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-01/metorex-copper-output-from-ruashi-in-congo-to-drop-20-in-december-quarter.html
Metorex Ltd. said copper output in
the December quarter at its Ruashi mine in the Democratic
Republic of Congo is expected to be 20 percent lower than the
previous three months.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
